# topology

This file is a placeholder for the exported topology image (`topology.png`).

## How to Obtain

1. Complete the lab topology in Cisco Packet Tracer.
2. Export or screenshot the topology canvas.
3. Save the image as `topology.png` in this directory.

The image should clearly show all devices (SW1, SW2, PC1–PC4),
interface labels, VLAN assignments, and the trunk link between the switches.
